  "id": "RAW_74a5047c",
  "title": "硅基 AI 日报：阿里千问 APP 公测；曝华为将发布 AI 领域突破性技术",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTY1MjE2OA==&mid=2247491787&idx=2&sn=428e37ef423fdf2fcbead6f442fb283a",
  "date": "2025-11-17 08:13:00",
  "author": "乌鸦智能说",
  "siteName": "乌鸦智能说",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:unset;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 28px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"padding:8.5px 17px;max-height:none;z-index:auto;background-size:auto;visibility:visible;bottom:auto;clear:none;line-height:29.75px;min-height:0px;border-color:rgb(63, 63, 63);background-position:0% center;float:none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;background-repeat:repeat;background-clip:border-box;top:auto;left:auto;border-width:0px;background-image:none;border-style:none;height:auto;min-width:0px;\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">面向C端市场的AI产品迎来一家巨头布局。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">11月17日，阿里巴巴正式宣布“千问”项目，全力进军AI to C市场，基于全球性能第一的开源模型Qwen3的千问APP公测版上线，供用户免费使用。千问APP公测版已在各大应用商店上架，并同步提供网页和PC版。面向全球市场的千问APP国际版也将在近期上线。上线后十分火爆，千问APP一度崩溃。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">同时，另一家国内科技巨头也迎来了新突破。据媒体报道，华为将在 11 月 21 日发布 AI 领域的突破性技术，可将 GPU（图形处理器）、NPU（神经网络处理器）等算力资源的利用率，从行业平均的 30% 至 40% 提升至 70%，显著释放算力硬件潜能。该突破是通过软件创新实现英伟达、昇腾及其他三方算力的统一资源管理与利用，屏蔽算力硬件差异，为 AI 训练推理提供更高效的资源支撑。</span></p>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">过去一天，国内外AI行业还有更多热点可以关注，硅基君带你一起看看。</span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 01 /</span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">大模型</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）Grok 5 或延期至明年发布</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">据《The Information》报道，埃隆 · 马斯克宣布 xAI 将推迟 Grok 5 的发布至明年。（预计时间为 2026 年第一季度）</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">马斯克在周五的 Baron Capital 年度投资大会上表示，经过额外训练时间后，Grok 5 将在各项指标上「以显著优势成为全球最智能的 AI」，并强调该产品有望达到类人智能水平。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">xAI 成立于 2023 年春季，其核心产品为大型语言模型 Grok。马斯克在会上指出，Grok 5 的目标是「超越所有竞争对手」，并暗示该版本可能带来突破性的 AI 体验。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">他此前曾表示，该聊天机器人将「让人感觉具备感知能力」，并有机会实现人类级别的智能。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">值得一提的是，马斯克此前曾多次在 X 社交媒体上，表示将会在 2025 年年底前推出 Grok 5 模型，并自信其性能将「碾压」竞争对手的 GPT-5。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）Qwen Code 新版本上线</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">日前，通义千问宣布，Qwen Code v0.2.1 版本已正式上线。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">新版最大的变化，是正式开放了免费网络搜索能力。用户不再需要切换浏览器查资料，Qwen Code 可以直接在控制台调用 dashscope 完成在线检索，支持 Qwen OAuth 用户每月约 2000 次免费额度，代码查错、查文档、查依赖一条龙全部自动完成。这意味着开发者可以真正把知识检索与 IDE 工作流融合起来。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">此外，新版本也有以下升级：</span></p>\n       <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">代码编辑更精准：优化了代码编辑逻辑，通过模糊匹配降低错误率，减少重试次数；</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">更多控制：开放 temperature、top_p 和 max tokens 等参数配置，赋予用户更精细的控制权；</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">增加 Zed IDE 集成：支持任务与待办管理，提升开发流效率；</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">更干净的输出：工具响应格式简化为纯文本，AI理解更容易；</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">搜索功能全面增强：支持 .gitignore 过滤、文件智能筛选与命名标准化；</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">性能优化：包括零开销匹配、Unicode 处理优化及输出限制调整；</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"font-style:italic;letter-spacing:normal;\">\n         <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-style: italic;\">错误修复：修复多项兼容性与稳定性问题，全面适配 macOS 与 Windows 平台。</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n       </ul>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 6 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 02 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI应用</span></span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）阿里千问APP公测，与ChatGPT展开全面竞争</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">11月17日，阿里巴巴正式宣布“千问”项目，全力进军AI to C市场，基于全球性能第一的开源模型Qwen3的千问APP公测版上线，供用户免费使用。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">目前，千问APP公测版已在各大应用商店上架，并同步提供网页和PC版。面向全球市场的千问APP国际版也将在近期上线，借助Qwen模型的海外影响力与ChatGPT直接争夺海外用户。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">阿里管理层认为，AI发展将经历“学习人”、“辅助人”和“超越人”三个阶段。目前，大模型的能力已经进入到“辅助人”的Agentic AI时代，阿里大力入局C端市场的时机已经成熟。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">阿里方面表示，这次发布的千问APP是一个初级版本，将用最先进的模型，打造一个“会聊天能办事的个人AI助手”。除了聊天足够聪明外，“能办事”将是千问APP的一个重要发力方向。千问APP的战略目标是打造未来的AI生活入口。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）Meta 将引入「AI 使用」绩效考核</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">据《Business Insider》报道，Meta 将从 2026 年起在员工绩效考核中引入「AI 驱动影响」作为核心指标。公司内部备忘录显示，Meta 将评估员工如何利用 AI 提升生产力、推动工具开发及实现业务成果。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">Meta 人力负责人 Janelle Gale 表示，这一转变旨在推动企业迈向「AI 原生文化」，并奖励在工作或团队层面产生显著 AI 成果的员工。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">报道指出，Meta 已在招聘流程中允许候选人使用 AI 完成编码面试，并通过内部激励项目「Level Up」推动员工采用 AI。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">与此同时，公司还将在今年 12 月启动绩效评估周期，推出「AI Performance Assistant」工具，帮助员工撰写绩效反馈。员工可使用 Meta 内部 AI 助手 Metamate 或 Google 的 Gemini 完成相关内容。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n           <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:center;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 03 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n           <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">投融资情报</span></span></strong></span></p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）AI+消费机器人公司「灵宇宙」再获2亿元PreA轮系列融资</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">11月17日，AI+消费机器人公司灵宇宙（上海灵宇宙科技发展有限公司）宣布，已于近期完成2亿元PreA轮系列融资。本轮融资由上海国际集团旗下国方创新、国泰海通、广发信德、滴滴出行、拉卡拉旗下考拉基金、润建股份等一众头部金融机构和上市公司参投，老股东超额追投。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">上海灵宇宙科技发展有限公司成立于2023年8月，创始人顾嘉唯曾担任百度深度学习研究院人机交互负责人、微软亚洲研究院研究员，2016年入选麻省理工科技评论MIT TR35全球科技创新家。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">作为一家专注于人工智能与人机交互的创新科技公司，灵宇宙致力于为全球家庭及个人用户打造“伙伴型”AI机器人产品，重塑人机交互方式。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">灵宇宙的核心引擎在于其自主研发的LingOS交互操作系统。基于LingOS，灵宇宙打造的原生AI硬件产品“小方机”一经上市就登顶618期间AI玩具及玩具总榜双榜第一。在刚刚过去的双十一购物节，“小方机”在京东和天猫等多个平台的榜单中名列前茅，并再度获得京东AI玩具“品牌累计榜单”和“SKU累计榜单”双榜第一，销售额同比今年618期间增长超230%。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;line-height:1.75;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n           <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:center;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 04 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n           <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI基础设施</span></span></strong></span></p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）曝华为将发布 AI 领域突破性技术</span></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">据中国基金报消息，华为将在 11 月 21 日发布 AI 领域的突破性技术，有望解决算力资源利用效率的难题。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">具体来看，华为即将发布 AI 领域的突破性技术，可将 GPU（图形处理器）、NPU（神经网络处理器）等算力资源的利用率，从行业平均的 30% 至 40% 提升至 70%，显著释放算力硬件潜能。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">据透露，华为即将发布 AI 领域的突破性技术，是通过软件创新实现英伟达、昇腾及其他三方算力的统一资源管理与利用，屏蔽算力硬件差异，为 AI 训练推理提供更高效的资源支撑。</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总了阿里千问 APP 公测、华为 AI 算力突破、Grok 5 延期、Qwen Code 更新及 AI 投融资等近期国内外 AI 行业重要动态。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总了阿里千问 APP 公测、华为 AI 算力突破、Grok 5 延期、Qwen Code 更新及 AI 投融资等近期国内外 AI 行业重要动态。",
  "summary": "本篇“硅基 AI 日报”全面梳理了近期国内外人工智能领域的核心进展。其中，阿里巴巴正式宣布“千问”项目，推出基于 Qwen3 模型的“千问 APP”公测版，全面进军 AI to C 市场，目标是打造个人 AI 助手和 AI 生活入口。同时，华为预告将发布一项 AI 领域突破性技术，通过软件创新显著提升 GPU/NPU 算力利用率至 70%，并实现多方算力统一管理，有望缓解 AI 算力瓶颈。此外，文章还提及 xAI 的 Grok 5 模型或将延期至明年发布，通义千问 Qwen Code 发布新版本，增强了网络搜索和代码编辑功能，以及 AI+消费机器人公司灵宇宙完成 2 亿元 PreA 轮融资，Meta 计划将 AI 使用纳入员工绩效考核等行业热点。",
